enemy1 tweak class
redef 1.5 tweak speed 

: *enemy ( - actor )
    class @ spawn ;

: come-down ( xratio. - )
    -radius from-top x 2!
    0 speed @ vx 2! ;

: come-up ( xratio. - )
    radius from-bottom x 2! 
    0 speed @ negate vx 2! ;

:event
    gamew gameh 0.75 0.5 2p* at
    s" bigbug" find-class one [[ ]] 

    begin        
    *enemy [[ 0.6 come-down ]]    
    timing @ delay
    *enemy [[ 0.7 come-up ]]
    timing @ delay
    *enemy [[ 0.8 come-down ]]    
    timing @ delay
    *enemy [[ 0.9 come-up ]]
    timing @ 4 * delay
    again
; 